ANNOUNCEMENT — Buckland & Gun arrives in London

Buckland & Gun is proud to announce its expansion into London, led by Founder Nick Buckland.

After 17 successful years operating across Australia  and having established a presence in New Zealand over the past 12 months  the company is now opening its London base as Nick returns to England to further develop opportunities for actors around the world.

This next chapter marks an exciting step in Buckland & Gun’s ongoing mission:
to support, represent, and elevate diverse, professionally trained actors across global markets.

Further updates will be released in the coming days, including:

Open castings to build the new London talent book

Professional audition workshops

Details of the upcoming booking and enrolment system

Buckland & Gun is delighted to begin this new journey in one of the world’s great creative capitals.

Welcome to the London chapter.

Buckland and Gun - AU  Buckland and Gun - NZ 
#bucklandandgun #londonactors #casting #ActingOpportunities

items.text:
Location: Either near Irvine, CA or Ontario, CA
Shoot Dates: December 3, 4, or 5
Time Commitment/Shoot Length: 3-4 Hours 
Compensation: $100 flat for 3–4 hours + a meals or snacks/drinks 

Project Type: I’m a sports medicine/orthopedic professional, not a filmmaker, but I’ve been tasked with producing an updated educational video for use in college classrooms. I’m looking for an outgoing, open-minded, athletic female model/actress (18–30) to participate in this short film that illustrates the accessibility and mobility challenges someone experiences during a temporary leg injury. All equipment (crutches, splint/cast) is provided. The cast is non-permanent and applied/removed safely.

About the Role:
You’ll portray someone recovering from a short-term lower-limb injury while navigating everyday environments—stores, stairs, hallways, buildings—using crutches and a removable cast/splint. The filming will take place over 3–4 hours in one day and will be edited to appear as multiple days. You will be responsible for your own makeup/wardrobe but we can discuss what is expected!

Creative Collaboration:
Because I’m approaching this from a healthcare perspective rather than a filmmaking one, I welcome creative input and collaboration. If you have ideas, insights, or personal experience that could make the scenes more realistic or engaging, I’m very open to incorporating them.

Who I’m Looking For:
Female, 18–30
Athletic, active, or fitness-oriented
Comfortable with walking non weight bearing on crutches
Good on camera and able to portray authentic emotion (pain, irritation, joy, etc.)
Able to bring a few outfit options and personal items (e.g., backpack, different outfits)
Acting/modeling experience not required
Experience with crutches or prior injuries is a plus
Based in Southern California

Project Details
Amateur, non-union
Educational, documentary-style
Mostly improvised with some guidance
Small, supportive, low-pressure environment
Opportunity to contribute creatively

To Apply
Please DM me, comment below, or email brettsmithh316@gmail.com with:
Your name + age
Headshot and full-body photo
A short intro about you addressing relative experience (video recording preferred)
Relevant experience (acting, sports, crutches/cast experience)
Your availability Dec 3, 4, or 5

Thanks!

🎬 **CASTING CALL – “THE BIRDS ARE CHIRPING” (PAID)**

📍 **Location:** Melbourne, VIC
📅 **Casting Date:** TBC
🎥 **Shoot Type:** Short Film
💰 **Compensation:** Paid
🗣 **Language:** Slovak (Preference given to Slovak or Czech actors, though familiarity with Slavic languages is sufficient.)

A tense, atmospheric psychological short film set in Czechoslovakia, following a young woman haunted by visions of an imposing KGB spy as she searches for the truth behind her past.

**ROLES AVAILABLE**

🎭 **ZUZANNA**
*Female Presenting | 18–25*
Outspoken, rebellious, and driven by strong beliefs. Her world fractures as paranoia surrounding her father grows into a spiralling psychological descent.

🎭 **FILIP**
*Male Presenting | 40s–50s*
Worn down by years under an oppressive regime. Emotionally numb but deeply devoted to giving his daughter the freedom he never had.

🎭 **JOZEF**
*Male Presenting | 30s–50s*
A chilling, ever-present KGB spy with a disturbing confidence and sinister smile. An almost otherworldly force silently stalking the story’s edges.

**PROJECT TONE**

A moody, slow-burning psychological journey blurring memory and paranoia.
Rooted in Cold War-era tension, the film explores identity, fear, and the fragile bond between a father and daughter as reality begins to fracture.

📩 **HOW TO APPLY**

Apply via **Actors and Extras** as a **Talent PRO member with a 1-month FREE trial**:
➡️ [https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls](https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls)

Create your free profile and get notified of new roles in your area!
Visit [https://www.actorsandextras.com](https://www.actorsandextras.com).

🔍 *This casting has been shared by Actors and Extras as a service to our talent directory members. We have received permission to share it and believe it to be legitimate. However, we strongly encourage all applicants to exercise due diligence and independently verify the details of the project before proceeding.*

items.text: Proud to share this next chapter  bringing Buckland & Gun home to Great Britain

sharedPost.text:
ANNOUNCEMENT — Buckland & Gun arrives in London

Buckland & Gun is proud to announce its expansion into London, led by Founder Nick Buckland.

After 17 successful years operating across Australia  and having established a presence in New Zealand over the past 12 months  the company is now opening its London base as Nick returns to England to further develop opportunities for actors around the world.

This next chapter marks an exciting step in Buckland & Gun’s ongoing mission:
to support, represent, and elevate diverse, professionally trained actors across global markets.

Further updates will be released in the coming days, including:

Open castings to build the new London talent book

Professional audition workshops

Details of the upcoming booking and enrolment system

Buckland & Gun is delighted to begin this new journey in one of the world’s great creative capitals.

Welcome to the London chapter.

Buckland and Gun - AU  Buckland and Gun - NZ 
#bucklandandgun #londonactors #casting #ActingOpportunities

media.ocrText: May be a graphic of text that says 'A BUCKLAND & GUN ARRIVES IN LONDON After 17 years championing actors across Australia and recently expanding into New Zealand- Buckland & Gun is opening a new chapter in Loron. Founder Nick Buckland is returning home to England with a simple mission: to open doors for actors around the world and help emerging and established performers find meaningful opportunities across film, television, theatre, commercial work, and voice. We're thrilleo to be here. More soon. BUCKLAND. GUN'

items.title: Hi all,

items.text:
CASTING CALL – STARFARM 

We’re casting fun, stylish young women (15–25) for an unscripted eco-reality series!

AI is taking over the world. Replacing jobs, replacing people, reforming industries. They are humanity's greatest creation yet our ultimate competition. Now, an unscripted eco-reality series featuring 10 young women, learning to live on a completely remote and self-sustainable farm - across the dirt road, lies another self-sustained farm; run by AI. Will they survive or thrive? Will they change the future for the next generation of girls, by proving something woman-powered can be more fruitful than something AI-powered?

Do you have :
* 
**STRONG SENSE OF PERSONAL STYLE AND CREATIVE CONFIDENCE**
* 
**PASSION FOR FASHION, ART, FILM, TV, MUSIC VIDEOS OR DIGITAL CONTENT**
* 
**LOVE FOR ANIMALS, OR AN INTEREST IN SOCIAL/ENVIRONMENTAL CAUSES**

Think: The Simple Life x Ready Player One

Filming in BAY AREA, remote filming roles open too

Nationwide applicants encouraged to apply (travel & accommodations provided).

Total Pay: US$1,750 (est. 5 days of work)

TO APPLY:

Email themadelynx@gmail.com

Subject: *STAR FARM – Your Name, Age*

Include: Name, age, location + recent photo (headshots appreciated, not required) + short intro.

items.text:
**Szukam modelki na zasadzie TFP  Gliwice/Katowice ( Śląsk )  **

 

   Szukam pań które nie krępują się własnego ciała i chciałaby mieć ciekawą pamiątkę w postaci klimatycznych zdjęć.  Wiem jak bardzo jest ważna akceptacja własnego ciała bo przez to też możemy inaczej funkcjonować. Przez takie zdjęcia można również tego dokonać. Sesja w głównej mierze jest jako taki motywator.

 

Poszukuje kobiety w **wieku od 30 **lat nie koniecznie z doświadczeniem pozowania,  na zasadach Tfp mieszkającej w Gliwicach lub okolicach Zabrze czy Katowice najdalej. Posiadam na wyposażeniu mini studio z kilkoma tłami oraz lampami. Mam również duży wybór kostiumów i gadżetów do wykorzystywania. Główny motyw do kobieta: Piękna i drapieżna! Sama sesja trwa przeważnie od 1,5h do 2h w zalezności od motywów.

** **

**Temat 1 – ‘’Kobieta mafii 1930’’**

Postać kobiety osadzona w 1930 roku w roli bogatej kobiety, która trudni się gangsterstwem. Przewidziane są ujęcia m.in. przy stoliku na którym są pieniądze, wino, rewolwer. Tło jest wydrukowane w formie muru, cegieł. Motyw sensualny.

 

**Temat 2 – ‘’Wampirzyca w baroku 1700’’**

Postać kobiety ubrana najpierw w suknie czarną oraz peleryne z kapturem. Do tego czarna długa peruka oraz czarne paznokcie. W kolejnym etapie sesji motyw sensualny.

 

**Temat 3 – ‘’Duchy lasu’’**

Postać kobiety ubrana w wianek i w pelerynę z otwartym przodem. W dłoni ma zakrwawiony sierp. Usta czarne oraz paznokcie.

 

**Temat 4 – ‘’Kleopatra’’**

Postać kobiety z czarna peruką w stylu Kleopatry. W prawej recę trzymac będzie berło Anubisa a w drugiej ręcę księgę umarłych. Na biodrach będzie mieć jedynie klasyczne odzienie z 2 części. Na klatce piersiowej założony będzie napierśnik złoty.

 

https://www.maxmodels.pl/lukus_wielki2

**Zapraszam na stronę Facebook Łukasz Magiera – Fotografia**

 

Więcej informacji na Priv

items.text:
Szukam ekipy aktorskiej do przygotowania około godzinnego spektaklu dla młodzieży (8. klasa oraz 1–2 klasa liceum). Najważniejsze, aby przedstawienie było ciekawe i angażujące dla tej grupy wiekowej.

📅 Termin: 16 grudnia
⏰ Godzina: raczej poranna — 9:30 lub 10:00 (do ustalenia jeszcze z dyrektorem w razie czego)
💰 Budżet: 2100 zł
🎭 Obsada: np. 3 aktorów — ale jesteśmy otwarci na propozycje
📍Rzecz będzie miała miejsce w MOK Sulejów, natomiast ewentualne próby będą w Łodzi

Jeśli macie gotowy spektakl, który pasowałby do młodzieży, chętnie go rozważymy!
Jeśli nie — nie ma problemu. Szukamy przede wszystkim osób chętnych, a scenariusz wybierzemy lub stworzymy wspólnie. 😊
W przyszłości planujemy także promować i sprzedawać ten projekt dalej, więc może to być fajna okazja do współpracy na dłużej.

Zainteresowani? Napiszcie na priv do mnie - 

Gabriela Juszczak

items.summary:
Szukam ekipy aktorskiej do przygotowania około godzinnego spektaklu dla młodzieży (8. klasa oraz 1–2 klasa liceum). Najważniejsze, aby przedstawienie było ciekawe i angażujące dla tej grupy wiekowej.

📅 Termin: 16 grudnia
⏰ Godzina: raczej poranna — 9:30 lub 10:00 (do ustalenia jeszcze z dyrektorem w razie czego)
💰 Budżet: 2100 zł
🎭 Obsada: np. 3 aktorów — ale jesteśmy otwarci na propozycje
📍Rzecz będzie miała miejsce w MOK Sulejów, natomiast ewentualne próby będą w Łodzi

Jeśli macie gotowy spektakl, który pasowałby do młodzieży, chętnie go rozważymy!
Jeśli nie — nie ma problemu. Szukamy przede wszystkim osób chętnych, a scenariusz wybierzemy lub stworzymy wspólnie. 😊
W przyszłości planujemy także promować i sprzedawać ten projekt dalej, więc może to być fajna okazja do współpracy na dłużej.

Zainteresowani? Napiszcie na priv do mnie - 

Gabriela Juszczak 

https://www.facebook.com/share/16nAsP7acb/?mibextid=wwXIfr

We will be a team of three person, two coming from London (director, producer), one (myself, music producer) from Berlin. We would like to invite one interested Actor/actress, (film) Producer, distributor etc. Please feel free to DM with your (professional) profile. With this free ticket, our main intension is t network, getting to know, have an evening of work and fun, possible future collaboration. Thanks, Sending many greetings

sharedPost.text:
Der Kino Mittwoch auf radioYpsilon 

MOVIETIME KW 49/2025

FREDDYS PIZZERIA ERÖFFNET ERNEUT UND GLOBALE ÖKOLOGISCHE HERAUSFORDERUNGEN 

Vor nicht langer Zeit sorgten die animatronischen Figuren für Schrecken, nun hat die wohl bekannteste Pizzeria wieder geöffnet in FIVE NIGHTS AT FREDDY'S 2 (Stadtkinocenter Laa,  Babylon Kino Horn und Filmbühne Waidhofen/Ybbs).

Regisseur Othmar Schmiderer beleuchtet unter anderem die Ökosysteme in Mitteleuropa in seiner Doku Elements Of(f) Balance. Wie der Film entstanden ist erzählt er uns in einem ausführlichen Interview. 

Die 77jährige Tereza bricht auf der Suche nach der Erfüllung ihrer letzten Wünsche in das Amazonasgebiet auf in DAS TIEFSTE BLAU (Kronenkino Mistelbach).

Weitere Filmtipps sowie die Kinocharts und Weihnachtshits aus Filmen die man kennt,  präsentiert Ihnen Sarah Fuchs. 

Mittwoch 3.12.25 von 18 bis 19h auf radioYpsilon 94.5 oder via Stream (http://mp3.radioypsilon.at:8000/)

message.text:
Weihnachten beginnt am Sonntag mit dem 1. Advent. Zu der Zeit ist auch `Gospel in the Air´! Hier ein schönes Stück, gespielt von CLASSIC MEETS JAZZ mit der professionellen Mezzosopranistin Annette Kuhn und Jo Flinner als Begleitung am Piano. Das Stück wurde vor einiger Zeit in einer Probe aufgenommen.

----------------AMAZING GRACE----------------------
Wir wünschen einen besinnlichen und schönen Advent!     🙂

items.text:
Location: Berlin

Shooting: mid-January

None paid (student project) + food + footage reel

ROLE HELEN (Lead, playing age 23-30)

Helen is the daughter of Hades, living in the mortal world in isolation.

She’s observant, emotionally detached on the surface, but with a complex inner world.

Her energy is quiet, intense, and unpredictable; she feels outside of humanity while desperately

studying it.

She is not a stereotype “strong female lead”.

She is layered, morally grey, dry, curious, bitter, vulnerable, and intimidating without trying.

A character who barely shows her emotions but feels everything deeply.

This role requires:

● strong subtle acting

● microexpressions

● comfort with psychological + mystical scenes

● ability to play someone who is always scanning her surroundings

● comfort acting opposite horror elements (no gore, more psychological/supernatural)

No previous fantasy experience needed, just strong emotional control and complexity.

All ethnicities welcome.

ABOUT THE PROJECT 

This is a 30-minute TV pilot for my graduation project and a proof-of-concept.

The tone is similar to The Sandman, Pan’s Labyrinth, and Only Lovers Left Alive; dark, poetic,

mythological, grounded in emotional realism.

The story explores:

● Mythology incorporated into modern Berlin

● Identity and isolation

● Power structures

● Neurodivergent perception

● The horror of being watched by the divine

Helen is the center of this world.

We offer a complex role with depth and high-quality footage for your acting reel. As stated

before, this is a proof-of-concept pilot episode. The goal is to apply for further funding and production support in 2026 and continue the series.

REQUIREMENTS

● Based in Berlin or able to travel.

● Availability for shooting in mid-January.

● Comfortable with night scenes and horror tones.

● Able to commit to rehearsals in December.

TO APPLY!!

Send to: celia.t@catalyst-students.com

● Recent headshot or clear photo.

● Showreel (if available).

● Your age + where you are based.

MUSICIANS WANTED – SUMMER 2026 IN GREECE

We are seeking talented solo and duo musicians to perform in our 5★ partner resorts in Greece during the Summer 2026 season (May–October).  You will be required to perform 4 sets of 45 minutes, 6 times a week.

Pianists, violinists, saxophonists, guitarists, singers, or musical duos offering elegant live performances are welcome to apply.

WE OFFER
 • 6-month contracts in luxury resorts
 • Competitive monthly salary based on experience and skills
 • Free accommodation, meals, and beverages
 • Flight reimbursement up to €300 and airport transfer

REQUIREMENTS
 • Professional solo or duo musicians ready to perform live
 • Wide and versatile repertoire (jazz, lounge, pop, classical, etc.)
 • Own instruments and performance attire (resort-appropriate style)
 • Only  EU passports !
        

APPLY NOW
Send your promo video to: 

adriano@palmera-agency.com

Witam
Jestem aktorem serbskimmieszkahacym w Warszawie ponad 30 lat.
Mam bardzo duże doświadczenie w pracy przed kamerami.
Występowałem w kilku filmach polskiej i zagranicznej produkcji, w kilku serialach, telediskach, .innych projektach filmowych jak i w ponad 40 reklam z czego połowa to główne roly oly.
Oprócz aktorstwem zajmuje się również muzyka,.mallarstwiem artystycznym, grałem profesjonalnie piłkę nożną dla Partizan Belgrad, dla reprezentacji Serbii i Yugoslawii, jak i reprez notacji polskich aktorów.
Zapraszam do współpracy
Fejsbuk Jasmin Soljanin 
i Jasmin Soljanin malarstwo 
Tel. 601 666 116
e-mail jasminsoljanin.art@gmail.com

items.text:
🎥 DOP / Video Creator — Poznań / Warszawa — Komercyjne projekty & Art-Movement

Cześć,

Nazywam się Vasilij Marinich i od ponad 3 lat pracuję jako DOP / Główny Operator Obrazu oraz Full-Cycle Video Creator (koncept → światło → kamera → montaż → color grading).

Specjalizuję się w estetyce kinowej bliskiej fashion film, movement, art-house i reklamie emocjonalnej.

Pracuję na sprzęcie Sony FX3 + RS4 Pro, własnym oświetleniu oraz DaVinci Resolve Studio (zaawansowany color grading).

Baza: Poznań
Realizacje: cała Polska (często Warszawa)

Współpracuję przy:
• kreatywnych projektach komercyjnych
• teledyskach
• produkcjach fashion & movement
• reklamach i social content
• artystycznych projektach filmowych

Jeśli szukasz operatora, który potrafi zbudować światło, rytm i emocję w kadrze — zapraszam do kontaktu.

Portfolio (Vimeo): https://vimeo.com/marinichfilms?fl=pp&fe=sh
Showreel:  https://vimeo.com/1073969838?fl=pl&fe=sh
IG: https://www.instagram.com/dop_marinich_pl/

Chętnie podejmę współpracę.
Piszę na priv lub dop.marinich@gmail.com.

—
DOP | Full-Cycle Creator
Poznań / Warszawa

**CASTING CALL - MAND I SPILLEALDER 35-45**

Vi er en gruppe fra Multiplatform Storytelling & Production, som er i gang med vores første semesterprøve. 

Det bliver en historie der skildrer menneskelighed, status og empati, i en komisk, surrealistisk, ekspressiv thriller. 

**Castingprocessen** vil foregå således at vi stiller en lille selftape opgave, og ud fra den vil kalde ind til casting der ligger enten onsdag eller torsdag i næste uge.

Derefter vil vi ønske en læseprøve med instruktør om fredagen, eller hvornår det passer med cast, og til sidst med optagelsesdage tirsdag til torsdag ugen efter det.

*Da det er en skoleproduktion er det desværre ikke et lønnet job, men der vil være mad og forfriskning på set, samt en god stemning med unge engagerede filmskabere. 

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig!

items.text:
CASTING CALL

For upcoming Non-Union Series, ANCIENT BODIES SEASON 2.

Looking for 

Egyptian People, All Genders, and All Ages 

Non-Union Only
Rate: $200 per day
Manitoba Residents Only (MUST have SIN #) 
Filming in Winnipeg and the surrounding areas December 11 to 19. 
Must have full day and evening availability 

Please email info@oafilmstudio.com with the subject line: 
Egyptian Person_YOUR NAME

Send the following info:
- Full Name
- Age
- Gender
- Ethnicity
- Height
- Phone
- Email Address
- State that you are non-union and a Manitoba resident with a SIN# and work permit
- Your availability from December 11-19 (Must be available all day and evening)
- State if you have tattoos
- Do you have your own transportation or a reliable ride?
- If you have any acting or performance experience, let us know (Speaking, SOC, Background, Theatre, Public speaking, Social Media). No experience is alright.
- 2 Current (TAKEN DAY OF SUBMISSION) Photos (1 selfie & 1 Full Body Shot)

Please share!

#Winnipeg #winnipegcastingcall #WinnipegActing
Onalee Ames Film Studio 
150 Stafford, Winnipeg, MB

items.text:
CASTING CALL 

03/12/25

The Party No One Wanted (Short Film)

**A dark comedy about grief and family relationships.**

Robbie and Mary have to get through an excruciating memorial that has a DJ, karaoke and a pregnancy announcement / gender reveal planned by their half sister Lisa.

* Shooting in March in TW19
* Auditions in Elephant and Castle but also accepting self tapes
* Travel Expenses Paid
* Student film being Shown in the BFI and hoping to go to Film festivals
* See poster for main roles **go to bottom for other roles **

Email: [tylerb170805@gmail.com](mailto:tylerb170805@gmail.com)  for further details

I will include the script and auditioning process in my email back to you, please note over the Christmas period there will be a pause in my emailing however casting won’t close till the end of January or until all roles are filled.

**There is also:**
* Bill (50s-60s)
* Annie (40s+)
* DJ (40s+)
* Daniel (35+)
* Gladis (40+)
* Peter (40+)
* Keith (50+)
* James (30s)

Hello! I’m one of the producers at Pipmonk, a London-based production company. Our team is currently casting for a lead role in a drama short film. We’re looking for a British-Chinese male aged 25-30. Please note the ability to speak both English and Cantonese language is required! Please see more details in the attachment below.

Contact email: 

framedbetweentwo.movie@gmail.com

Casting British- British-Chinese Chinese male, aged 25-30 for a lead role a drama short film. Filming Hong Kong unit: late Feb or early March 2026 (subject to change). Travel and accommodation expenses covered by production. Filming London unit: May 2026 (subject to change). Ability to speak both English and Cantonese language is required. 🎥 Title: To Kiss a Boy�📍 Filming in: Tacoma, WA�📅 Dates: Tentative �💰 Paid | Non-Union | Meals +Travel + Credit Provided

About the Film:�A heartfelt romance between a queer woman and a trans man exploring love, identity, and learning to be proud of who you are — and who you love.

�Small crew, intimate vibe, safe set.

ROLES:

💫 JASMINE (Lead) 

* Black woman, late 20s–30s.

* Creative, confident, guarded yet deeply loving.

🎬 Details:

* 7-day shoot, minimal locations (museum, apartment, bar, cars, gas station).

* Includes 1 love scene — filmed respectfully, closed set. NO NUDITY.

* Light emotional tone, intimate storytelling.

To Submit:�📧 Email: tokissaboyfilm@gmail.com�📝 Subject: [Role] – [Your Name]�📸 Include: Headshot, reel or short monologue, and a short note about why this story resonates with you. New talent welcome. 

Director’s Note:�We’re building something tender, real, and authentic. A story about queer love that feels seen.

Caped Crusader Parties is looking for new superhero and princess performers to join our growing team! If you love performing, entertaining kids and bringing big energy to events, we want to hear from you!

We’ve got lots of work coming up for the right people. We’re based mainly in London & Essex, but we deliver parties and events all over the UK. ✨

We’re proud partners of Tour International Rugby Festivals, providing character entertainment at events nationwide. 🏉
We’re also experts in children’s entertainment, trusted by families, schools and community organisations — just check our 5⭐ reviews!

✅ Great rates of pay
✅ Costumes & training provided
✅ Supportive team environment
✅ Exciting variety of events

If you’re confident, reliable, great with kids and love performing, send us a DM or call 📞 07535 822338 to apply!

Let’s make magic ✨

items.text:
🎬 **NOW CASTING – Video Presenters (London SE11 5DP)**

🎥 **1. Female Presenter (Product Demo Video)**

💼 **Role:** Present and demonstrate a new mobile app in a short product video

📍 **Location:**  London SE11 5DP
💰 **Rate:** £150 (flat fee, includes travel & prep)
🕒 **Time:** Half-day shoot (4 hours total)

**Requirements:**
* White female, native English speaker
* Confident, energetic, and natural on camera
* Able to explain product features clearly and engagingly
* Punctual and professional
* Reference: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aMbvkxcpjTw

**To Apply:**
Please send these to ginfx@growinmkt.uk
1️⃣ A recent professional photo
2️⃣ A **30-second video self-introduction** (show your energy and clarity)
3️⃣ Links to any previous presentation or demo work (if available)

-----

🎙 **2. Male Presenter (News / TikTok-Style Content)**

💼 **Role:** Host short videos discussing news and trending topics with energy, humor, and charisma.

📍 **Location:** London SE11 5DP
💰 **Rate:** £15/hour (approx. £100/day)
🕒 **Schedule:** Flexible hourly bookings

**Requirements:**
* Black male, fluent English, clear pronunciation
* Expressive speaking style (not monotone)
* Friendly or witty personality preferred
* Professional appearance (black suit required)
* Confident on camera or microphone
* Reference: https://vm.tiktok.com/ZNdvvmTVG/

**To Apply:**
Please send these to ginfx@growinmkt.uk
1️⃣ A short **voice demo or self-intro video**
2️⃣ Your **availability and contact details**

items.text:
Come and join our friendly and welcoming festive dance class, designed for total beginners!

We meet every Monday (and from January 22nd, Thursdays too!) But for 8/12 & 15/12 we are getting Christmassy! We’ll be having fun, learning a simple routine across the two sessions to the absolute BANGER that is CANDY CANE LANE by Sia. 🙌

This is the perfect way to try the session out, have a little fun with your mates, make some new ones and get in the festive mood! And why not grab at drink at the bar after!? (Be rude not to! 💃🪩🕺🏻) 

Festive fancy dress heavily encouraged for the 2nd of the classes on the 15/12! 

Drop us a FB message or email enquiries@glsdance.co.uk to pay your £3 deposit and join the crew!

This is the perfect way to try the session out, have a little fun with your mates, make some new ones and get in the festive mood! And why not grab at drink at the bar after!? (Be rude not to! 💃🪩🕺🏻) 

Festive fancy dress heavily encouraged for the 2nd of the classes on the 15/12! 

Drop us a FB message or email enquiries@glsdance.co.uk to pay your £3 deposit and join the crew!

**ARU Record** poszukuje aktora z dojrzałym, niskim głosem do odegrania postaci **Gustava** z serii ***Metal Family***! Postać pojawia się w dwóch odcinkach, a jeden z nich mamy już niemal ukończony - brakuje nam tylko Gustava.
## Wymagania:
> 
* Mikrofon **dobrej** jakości.
* Dobre warunki akustyczne (brak pogłosu / echa).
* Większe doświadczenie z aktorstwem lub fandubbingiem.
* Terminowość.
* Dobra dykcja.

W celu zgłoszenia się zapraszam do mnie na pv!
EDIT:
Chętnych zapraszam na serwer Discord - ARU Record [https://discord.gg/CM8PjSVgjX](https://discord.gg/CM8PjSVgjX)

attachments.ocrText: Może być zdjęciem przedstawiającym tekst

sharedPost.text:
Szukam starszej, sympatycznej Pani z Krakowa, która chciałaby wziąć udział w krótkim, świątecznym spocie reklamowym o Szlachetnej Paczce. 🌟

Chodzi o wzruszającą scenę: wspólna rozmowa na ławce, trochę ciepła, trochę świątecznej magii… a na koniec symboliczne podzielenie się opłatkiem. 🎄✨  

Zdjęcia będą realizowane w przyjemnej, spokojnej atmosferze, a całość ma piękny i szlachetny przekaz.

Jeśli znacie kogoś — babcię, ciocię, sąsiadkę — która mogłaby się odnaleźć w takiej roli, bardzo proszę o kontakt. ❤️

Dziękuję!

items.text:
PILNE !!! - WARSZAWA !!! - GLINIARZE !!!

Do grudniowego odcinka serialu „Gliniarze” realizowanego w Warszawie (i bliskich okolicach) wciąż poszukuję kobiety do następującej roli:

Hostessa 1 (23) – pracuje w agencji towarzyskiej u Makara. Zostaje pobita przez Makara, gdy nie chce spełnić wyuzdanych żądań klienta. 1 PLAN

Epizod z tekstem
Sceny: 11A, 12 
Data: 08.12
Stawka: 350 zł netto

Chętne Panie zapraszam do wysyłania pilnych zgłoszeń na adres: casting.outset@interia.pl

W tytule maila proszę o wpisanie nazwy postaci.

W treści maila proszę o zawarcie następujących informacji:
1. Wiek/wzrost/waga
2. Nr tel. Do kontaktu
3. Krótki opis doświadczenia
4. Linki do sowich materiałów video – demo/wizytówka/scenki castingowe
5. Aktualne zdjęcie
6. Informacje o posiadanym i czynnym prawie jazdy lub jego braku
7. Inormacje o ukończonej szkole aktorskiej/kursach

Nie zwracamy kosztów dojazdu/noclegu

Szukamy osób z Warszawy do głównych ról krótkometrażowego filmu realizowanego przez młodych twórców!

Doświadczenie aktorskie niewymagane, ale mile widziane.

Planowane zdjęcia: 2-6 stycznia 2026 (zajmą pewnie 3 dni)

Chłopak 1:

Wiek: 19-24 lata

Typ artysty w szaliku, który chodzi na noce poezji. 

Chłopak 2: 

Wiek: 19-24 lata

Chłopak, który wcieli się w role baristy.

Dziewczyna:

Wiek: 19-24 lata

Tzw ,,manic pixie dream girl", kobieca i czuła, interesuje się sztuką. Ekscentryczna i pewna siebie. Charakterystyczny wizerunek!

Po informacje prosimy się zgłaszać podając kod klienta na adres marketing@atvfilm.pl do dnia jutrzejszego - wtorek 2.12 do godz. 16 (Z TYTUŁEM FILM STUDENCKI)osoby które nie mają kodu klienta a chcą uczestniczyć w naszych castingach prosimy najpierw o wysłanie zgłoszenia poprzez naszą stronę [[https://galeriatwarzy.pl/zgloszenie](https://galeriatwarzy.pl/zgloszenie?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAYnJpZBEwMTBtR0pXZW96TkE1ZmdoeHNydGMGYXBwX2lkEDIyMjAzOTE3ODgyMDA4OTIAAR4Fb_iBJtPZvu51UQieuy_4WI1U_oQ6dB3CBMQQlqQ8Qgj853LQSmLj4dKWJw_aem_6yBdqndKb-kZe1CK2RjYFQ)]([https://galeriatwarzy.pl/zgloszenie](https://galeriatwarzy.pl/zgloszenie?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAYnJpZBEwMTBtR0pXZW96TkE1ZmdoeHNydGMGYXBwX2lkEDIyMjAzOTE3ODgyMDA4OTIAAR4S4Wb1a0tgSQpI7InPYtSfUp9RBbruacQ6PV5H6Y_TyCPdlMsU0fgJ65eqKQ_aem_YdS8OvnuPFWCVHUdXcxWPQ))

Zdjęcia 10.12

Szukam na plan reklamy osób z wizerunkiem.

Przymiarki mamy 9.12 a zdjęcia 10.12. 

Kobieta – ok 35 lat, 170 – 175 cm wzrostu, budowa ciała normalna

Kobieta – ok 35 lat, 165 – 170 cm wzrostu, budowa ciała normalna

Mężczyzna – ok 45 lat, 185 – 190 cm wzrostu, budowa ciała normalna

Kobieta – ok 40 lat, 180 – 185 cm wzrostu, budowa ciała normalna

Stawka za wszystko 1000 zł brutto-płatne przelewem  

Proszę zgłaszać się na adres - m.paziewska@stars-impresariat.pl w tytule proszę wpisać 10.12 reklama 

W mailu proszę umieścić- imię, nazwisko wiek tel oraz wyraźne zdjęcia.

Marta😃

items.text:
Warszawo 

Szukam na plan programu rozrywkowego osób które będą się świetnie bawiły, uśmiechały, robiły zdjęcia itp.

Plan  06.12 sobota 

Zdjecia w centrum w godzinach 8-12:30 maksymalnie.

Stawka 80 zł-płatne po planie.

Proszę wysyłać zgłoszenia na adres mailowy- m.paziewska@stars-impresariat.pl

W tytule proszę wpisać : program 06:12

Proszę w treści maila wpisać imię, nazwisko wiek tel oraz wyraźne zdjęcia.

Czekam na wasze zgłoszenia:)

Marta 😙

items.text:
Hello! I’m one of the producers at Pipmonk, a London-based production company. Our team is currently casting for a lead role in a drama short film. We’re looking for a British-Chinese male aged 25-30. Please note the ability to speak both English and Cantonese language is required! Please see more details in the attachment below.

Contact email: 

framedbetweentwo.movie@gmail.com

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of text that says '文興酒家 FOLRSEASONSGIUNESERESTALPART FOURSEASONSC CASTING CALL **PAID** ** Synopsis: A diasporic Hong Kong-born Londoner falls for visiting photographer. Sudden family grief forces him to confront his identity, choosing between his established life and estranged heritage. Casting British- British-Chinese Chinese male, aged 25-30 for a lead role a drama short film. Filming Hong Kong unit: late Feb or early March 2026 (subject to change). Travel and accommodation expenses covered by production. Filming London unit: May 2026 (subject to change). Ability to speak both English and Cantonese language is required. Please put subject as JUSTIN and email headshots to: :framedbetweentwo.movie@gmail.'

Benedictus quasi Deus' Interpretation von „Out of the dark“, das ein Falco Cover ist, ist recht ansprechend konzipiert, aber bisher nur als Youtube-Video verfügbar. Der Musiker beginnt mit sanften Panflötentönen und sein Gesang kommt anfangs sehr leise herüber. Dieses verstärkt die sehr innige Haltung. Später werden die Vocals rauer. Man kann also von einem Break sprechen. Energetische Effekte bringen einen besonderen und starken Touch hinein. 

Ein starker Bass verleiht dem Song einen rockigen Flair und das vorliegende Cover ist sehr interessant aufgebaut. Falcos Grundmelodie ist zu erkennen und Benedictus quasi Deus verfremdet das Original, so dass ich es als eine sehr gute Interpretation bezeichnen kann.  

Positiv herauszustellen ist auch in der Videodarstellung der Gebrauch von einer Kerze, Explosionen und Feuer, die ein dynamisches Ambiente hervorrufen.

Youtube-Video: https://youtu.be/gfvWL6h4GKk?si=YR5U2x_QCoWfQUfy

Roman Golub 
Northern Art Music - Bodystyler Musikmagazin

Ideal para ganar confianza, soltar el cuerpo y

mejorar el idioma

Un espacio cálido, creativo y 100% en español

CASA VEHU - Böszörményi út 4, 1126,

items.text:
CASTING CALL FOR STUDENT SHORT FILM (PAID) - AIRTIME 

Hi, we are students at Nottingham Trent University making a short film about a local live news broadcast minutes away from air where everything just keeps going wrong. The entire film will take place in one shot, or at least have the appearance it is.

📅Production date: January 2026

📍Location: Nottingham

💰Pay: Paid opportunity

🎥Production company: Nottingham Trent University (Student project)

ROLES AVAILABLE

🎭Character: Martin - The director of the morning news broadcast in *Airtime*. A crass man whose declining home life has driven him to becoming a functioning alcoholic whose grip on his own life is slipping, which is starting to affect his professional life as his apathy grows. Despite his plethora of problems, he can be an amicable personality in the right circumstances and is a skilled communicator and leader. Personality wise, he combines the jadedness of adulthood with a childlike disconnect between his actions/attitude and its effects on himself and other people around him.

👤Age Range: 35 - 50

🎯Type: Male Actor

🌍Ethnicity: White British

📌Based in or able to work in Nottingham, UK

🎭Character: Bethany - The assistant director in the morning news program in *Airtime*. She is highly professional and level-headed, oftentimes having to go beyond the call of duty due to the incompetence or indifference of the people around her. Bethany is very patient and would rather move the production along and work hard than waste time arguing with Martin or other members of the crew not pulling their weight. Despite her forbearance, she is finding it more difficult to bite her tongue as time goes on.

👤Age Range: 20 - 30

🎯Type: Female Actor

🌍Ethnicity: Open

📌Based in or able to work in Nottingham, UK

If anyone is interested or wants more information please DM me. 

Alternatively email me, [isaacoharefilm@gmail.com](mailto:isaacoharefilm@gmail.com)

Please include your age, headshot, and role you are applying for. We can’t wait to hear from you soon!

items.text:
Filmmakers! You're invited to our transformative meetup at Empowering Filmmakers! 

Every Saturday from 4-6pm in Los Angeles.

Join a vibrant community of aspiring filmmakers who are passionate about storytelling through narrative films. We aim to support one another in bringing our collective visions to life and creating movies together. By collaborating across different departments, we can harness each other's strengths and creativity. We all invest our energy and passion into each other’s projects and turn our individual ideas into a vibrant reality.

Our meetups foster creativity and connection, allowing you to collaborate with like-minded individuals. Whether you're a writer, actor, director, producer, or cinematographer, you will find support in honing your craft. Please note that we focus exclusively on narrative films.

Membership is FREE!.

Complete this form if you'd like to become a member.

https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScJPx3EyAE9HyemwIwzT-Q67ENY10I_nnWcbRZALch2wEo95w/viewform?usp=header

items.text:
LOGLINE: 

In a distant future, Callie Jones works as a hacker whose illegal activities draw the attention of the future's police force, potentially endangering their budding romance and their freedom.

WHO WE ARE LOOKING FOR:

Faye (she/her, trans-femme, 25-30) - Faye is an aspiring fashion designer and a close friend/ love interest to Callie. She is a gentle person who has plenty of love for anyone she meets, though even her patience has its limits. Years of living paycheque to paycheque in an unforgiving capitalist dystopia have her yearning for a stable life where she can be free to create and to love freely.

Shooting dates: Dec 1st, 2nd, 13th, 14th

Non union, paid work ($100 per day, open to negotiation), lunch provided.

Please send a headshot, resume, and demo reel (if applicable) to iamkarlyelyse@gmail.com

**Szukam modelki na zasadzie TFP  Gliwice/Katowice ( Śląsk )  **

 

   Szukam pań które nie krępują się własnego ciała i chciałaby mieć ciekawą pamiątkę w postaci klimatycznych zdjęć.  Wiem jak bardzo jest ważna akceptacja własnego ciała bo przez to też możemy inaczej funkcjonować. Przez takie zdjęcia można również tego dokonać. Sesja w głównej mierze jest jako taki motywator.

 

Poszukuje kobiety w **wieku od 30 **lat nie koniecznie z doświadczeniem pozowania,  na zasadach Tfp mieszkającej w Gliwicach lub okolicach Zabrze czy Katowice najdalej. Posiadam na wyposażeniu mini studio z kilkoma tłami oraz lampami. Mam również duży wybór kostiumów i gadżetów do wykorzystywania. Główny motyw do kobieta: Piękna i drapieżna! Sama sesja trwa przeważnie od 1,5h do 2h w zalezności od motywów.

** **

**Temat 1 – ‘’Kobieta mafii 1930’’**

Postać kobiety osadzona w 1930 roku w roli bogatej kobiety, która trudni się gangsterstwem. Przewidziane są ujęcia m.in. przy stoliku na którym są pieniądze, wino, rewolwer. Tło jest wydrukowane w formie muru, cegieł. Motyw sensualny.

 

**Temat 2 – ‘’Wampirzyca w baroku 1700’’**

Postać kobiety ubrana najpierw w suknie czarną oraz peleryne z kapturem. Do tego czarna długa peruka oraz czarne paznokcie. W kolejnym etapie sesji motyw sensualny.

 

**Temat 3 – ‘’Duchy lasu’’**

Postać kobiety ubrana w wianek i w pelerynę z otwartym przodem. W dłoni ma zakrwawiony sierp. Usta czarne oraz paznokcie.

 

**Temat 4 – ‘’Kleopatra’’**

Postać kobiety z czarna peruką w stylu Kleopatry. W prawej recę trzymac będzie berło Anubisa a w drugiej ręcę księgę umarłych. Na biodrach będzie mieć jedynie klasyczne odzienie z 2 części. Na klatce piersiowej założony będzie napierśnik złoty.

 

https://www.maxmodels.pl/lukus_wielki2

**Zapraszam na stronę Facebook Łukasz Magiera – Fotografia**

 

Więcej informacji na Priv

Szukam starszej, sympatycznej Pani z Krakowa, która chciałaby wziąć udział w krótkim, świątecznym spocie reklamowym o Szlachetnej Paczce. 🌟

Chodzi o wzruszającą scenę: wspólna rozmowa na ławce, trochę ciepła, trochę świątecznej magii… a na koniec symboliczne podzielenie się opłatkiem. 🎄✨  

Zdjęcia będą realizowane w przyjemnej, spokojnej atmosferze, a całość ma piękny i szlachetny przekaz.

Jeśli znacie kogoś — babcię, ciocię, sąsiadkę — która mogłaby się odnaleźć w takiej roli, bardzo proszę o kontakt. ❤️

Dziękuję!

items.text:
Hey zusammen 👋

ich teile das hier, weil ich weiß, wie hart unser Weg manchmal ist. Viele von uns geben alles, spielen gut und werden trotzdem nicht wirklich gesehen. Vielleicht hilft Dir das hier ein Stück weiter.

Ich habe einen kostenlosen 7 Tage E Mail Kurs erstellt. Jeden Tag bekommst Du eine kleine Übung, die Dir sofort etwas bringt und die Du ganz entspannt in Deinen Alltag einbauen kannst. Enthalten sind auch hilfreiche Tipps zu Castern, Agenturen und vielem, was uns Schauspielerinnen und Schauspieler wirklich beschäftigt.

Nach den 7 Tagen bekommst Du ein Jahr lang einmal pro Woche kurze Impulse zu Schauspiel, Präsenz, Mindset und auch Sichtbarkeit aus meiner eigenen Arbeit vor und hinter der Kamera.

Kurz zu mir, damit Du weißt, wer das hier teilt:

Ich bin Roberto aus München

🎭 international mehrfach ausgezeichnet als Schauspieler, Autor, Regisseur und Produzent
📽️ CEO der Lucky Eagle Production GmbH
🏆 Jurymitglied beim FilmHaus Berlin
🌍 arbeite seit Jahren in internationalen Film und Serienprojekten

Ich arbeite unglaublich gern mit Schauspielerinnen und Schauspielern und teile das Wissen, das mir selbst auf meinem Weg wirklich geholfen hat.

Wenn Du magst, findest Du hier den Kurs und ein Video, in dem ein paar meiner Mentees erzählen, wie sie meine Arbeit erlebt haben:

👉 kurs.nextstagecoaching.de

Vielleicht hilft es Dir oder jemandem aus Deinem Umfeld. Gib es gerne weiter, wenn es jemand brauchen kann ☺️

Und denk immer daran
Du bist genug. Genau jetzt. 🫶

Roberto

items.title: Hey zusammen 👋

items.text:
Vom Filmset ins echte Leben, Sergio Klee und Christian Weiße sprechen über Sicherheit, Wahrnehmung und Setkultur 

Wenn Veränderung den Blick schärft 

In diesem Teil erzählt Sergio Klee, wie persönliche Entwicklung die eigene Präsenz am Set verändert. Er beschreibt, wie innere Anspannung weicht, wenn man versteht, woher Nervosität wirklich kommt. Durch die Reflexion seines eigenen Weges zeigt er, wie Selbstkritik lauter sein kann als jedes Lob und weshalb Sicherheit erst entsteht, wenn man sich selbst erkennt statt sich zu verstecken. 

Wahrnehmung, Ego und die Kunst, nichts persönlich zu nehmen 

Sergio schildert eine Situation, in der er an einem Set offen äußerte, wo er sich wohlfühlt, und plötzlich in kritische Blicke lief. Er erklärt, wie schnell Menschen neutrale Aussagen bewerten und warum das Ego immer eine Wertung sucht, auch wenn keine da ist. 

Von Atmosphäre, Respekt und Kleinigkeiten mit grosser Wirkung 

Die Episode zeigt, wie unterschiedlich Drehtage wirken können. Sergio vergleicht Setkulturen, Catering, Umgangsformen und kleine Gesten, die den Unterschied zwischen distanziert und familiär ausmachen. Seine Erfahrungen bei Formaten wie Köln 50667, Alles was zählt, Barbara Salesch und Ulrich Wetzel machen deutlich, wie stark Wertschätzung das eigene Gefühl von Zugehörigkeit prägt und warum sich manche Orte sofort richtig anfühlen. 

Reinwachsen in Abläufe und Räume, bis die Kamera läuft 

Sergio beschreibt, wie man bei jedem neuen Projekt zuerst fremd wirkt, dann Orientierung findet und schließlich ankommt. Vom ersten Guten Tag im Büro über Kostüm und Maske bis zur laufenden Kamera zeigt er, wie viel Sicherheit in Wiederholung und Vorbereitung steckt. Das Gespräch öffnet einen seltenen Einblick in die leisen Momente vor dem Take, in denen man begreift, dass man dazugehört. 

Zu mir, Christian Weiße 

Ich bin Christian Weiße, Medienunternehmer, Content Creator und Inhaber der Karrideo Image- und Eventfilmproduktion aus Köln. Ich entwickle Bewegtbildformate, erzähle Geschichten für Unternehmen, Organisationen und Persönlichkeiten und kenne als Darsteller beide Seiten der Kamera. 

Abonniere den Kanal, like das Video, teile deine Gedanken in den Kommentaren und besuche mind_body_coach_ auf Instagram für weitere Impulse von Sergio Klee. 

Christian Weiße / Karrideo Imagefilm-Produktion / Karrideo Imagefilm-Produktion - Zuschauer, Auftraggeber, Partner

items.summary:
Vom Filmset ins echte Leben, Sergio Klee und Christian Weiße sprechen über Sicherheit, Wahrnehmung und Setkultur 

Wenn Veränderung den Blick schärft 

In diesem Teil erzählt Sergio Klee, wie persönliche Entwicklung die eigene Präsenz am Set verändert. Er beschreibt, wie innere Anspannung weicht, wenn man versteht, woher Nervosität wirklich kommt. Durch die Reflexion seines eigenen Weges zeigt er, wie Selbstkritik lauter sein kann als jedes Lob und weshalb Sicherheit erst entsteht, wenn man sich selbst erkennt statt sich zu verstecken. 

Wahrnehmung, Ego und die Kunst, nichts persönlich zu nehmen 

Sergio schildert eine Situation, in der er an einem Set offen äußerte, wo er sich wohlfühlt, und plötzlich in kritische Blicke lief. Er erklärt, wie schnell Menschen neutrale Aussagen bewerten und warum das Ego immer eine Wertung sucht, auch wenn keine da ist. 

Von Atmosphäre, Respekt und Kleinigkeiten mit grosser Wirkung 

Die Episode zeigt, wie unterschiedlich Drehtage wirken können. Sergio vergleicht Setkulturen, Catering, Umgangsformen und kleine Gesten, die den Unterschied zwischen distanziert und familiär ausmachen. Seine Erfahrungen bei Formaten wie Köln 50667, Alles was zählt, Barbara Salesch und Ulrich Wetzel machen deutlich, wie stark Wertschätzung das eigene Gefühl von Zugehörigkeit prägt und warum sich manche Orte sofort richtig anfühlen. 

Reinwachsen in Abläufe und Räume, bis die Kamera läuft 

Sergio beschreibt, wie man bei jedem neuen Projekt zuerst fremd wirkt, dann Orientierung findet und schließlich ankommt. Vom ersten Guten Tag im Büro über Kostüm und Maske bis zur laufenden Kamera zeigt er, wie viel Sicherheit in Wiederholung und Vorbereitung steckt. Das Gespräch öffnet einen seltenen Einblick in die leisen Momente vor dem Take, in denen man begreift, dass man dazugehört. 

Zu mir, Christian Weiße 

Ich bin Christian Weiße, Medienunternehmer, Content Creator und Inhaber der Karrideo Image- und Eventfilmproduktion aus Köln. Ich entwickle Bewegtbildformate, erzähle Geschichten für Unternehmen, Organisationen und Persönlichkeiten und kenne als Darsteller beide Seiten der Kamera. 

Abonniere den Kanal, like das Video, teile deine Gedanken in den Kommentaren und besuche mind_body_coach_ auf Instagram für weitere Impulse von Sergio Klee. 

Christian Weiße / Karrideo Imagefilm-Produktion / Karrideo Imagefilm-Produktion - Zuschauer, Auftraggeber, Partner

items.text:
📣 CASTING CALL  (ULØNNET - Intet budget)📣 

Vi er 6 passionerede filmstuderende fra Multiplatform Storytelling and Production, der søger to stærke mandlige skuespillere til vores kommende kortfilm – en original og visuelt ambitiøs fortælling med humor, varme og et strejf af det absurde. 

PROJEKTBESKRIVELSE 

LOGLINE: 
En ensom ældre mand på en gård forsøger på usædvanlige måder at skabe en forbindelse til sin nye nabo. Når kommunikation fejler, må handling tale. Men hvad sker der, når handlingen bliver… ret usædvanlig? En komedie med hjerte og kant om kommunikation, ensomhed og menneskelig kontakt. 

VI SØGER: 

📷 Mandlig skuespiller (65-80 år) – Svend Åge (Hovedrollen) 
En ensom, stædig og lidt sær mand, der længes efter selskab, men har svært ved at udtrykke det. Hans forsøg på kontakt er både rørende og komisk.

Vi er 6 passionerede filmstuderende fra Multiplatform Storytelling and Production, der søger to stærke mandlige skuespillere til vores kommende kortfilm – en original og visuelt ambitiøs fortælling med humor, varme og et strejf af det absurde.

En ensom ældre mand på en gård forsøger på usædvanlige måder at skabe en forbindelse til sin nye nabo. Når kommunikation fejler, må handling tale. Men hvad sker der, når handlingen bliver… ret usædvanlig? En komedie med hjerte og kant om kommunikation, ensomhed og menneskelig kontakt.

items.text:
Hallo ihr Lieben,

ich arbeite an einem Projekt, in dem ich Menschen interviewe, die mit unsichtbaren oder wenig bekannten Krankheiten leben – also Erkrankungen, die man nicht auf den ersten Blick sieht, die aber trotzdem den Alltag stark beeinflussen.

Mir ist wichtig, diesen Menschen eine Stimme zu geben: zu zeigen, was sie erleben, wie sie sich fühlen und was sich in unserer Gesellschaft vielleicht verändern sollte.

Wenn du selbst betroffen bist oder jemanden kennst, der mit einer solchen Krankheit lebt und offen darüber sprechen möchte, melde dich gerne bei mir.
Das Gespräch kann auf Wunsch anonym stattfinden.

Ich freue mich über jede Nachricht, jedes Vertrauen und jede Geschichte – ob groß oder klein.

Liebe Grüße
Polly

sharedPost.text:
Please read ALL INSTRUCTIONS before submitting.
If this post is live, then the roles are still available.

CASTING CALL (Los Angeles):
- Shoot date Monday, Dec. 8, 2025.
- Paid (Buyout, happy to share the right amount upon request￼).
- No guild/union affiliation.
- Video/Print/Social.
- For a medical office in Beverly Hills.
- DiSam FelmanSam Felman
- Preference to those with all day availability.

ROLES:
- Male identifying, age 35-50, clear skin, no facial hair, athletic/average build, caucasian or POC.

- (Soft hold availability only) Female identifying, age 35-45, clear skin, athletic/average build, caucasian or POC.

SUBMISSION INSTRUCTIONS:
Please do not submit unless you are available all day on Dec. 8, 2025.

STEP 1: Please take 4 pictures of yourself in natural light: 1) Facing forward. 2) Facing left. 3) Facing right. 4) Full body.

STEP 2: Please Facebook DM these piSam FelmanSam Felman along with your phone number, email address, and the word "Hippo".

STEP 3: Wait. You will be contacted either way. Please do not follow up.

THANK YOU!

CASTING CALL – Independent Short Film (LONDON)

We are casting for an upcoming student short film exploring obsession, ambition, and the dark side of the ballet world.

Production: Student film via The American University of Rome

Director: Maxine Sutton

Cinematographer: Georgia Blackson

Shooting Dates: December 12–19

ROLES

NATASHA (Lead)

Female, 18–28

Ballet-trained (advanced preferred)

Must convey vulnerability, intensity, and psychological depth

Strong acting, presence, and physical performance required

Slavic accent preferred.

Pay: 250€ flat rate for entire production

RUDOLPH

Male, 25–40

Dance experience preferred

Embodies both beauty and cruelty — a man who inspires awe, fear, and complete submission.

Slavic accent preferred.

Pay: 250€ flat rate for entire production

SYNOPSIS

Natasha, a talented but tormented ballerina, navigates a high-stakes audition that tests the limits of her physical and psychological endurance. As she strives for perfection under the watchful eye of the enigmatic Rudolph, the line between reality and terror begins to blur, forcing her to confront the true cost of ambition.

TO APPLY

Please complete the audition form and send it, along with a headshot, to: maxineclairesutton@gmail.com

**PAID OPPORTUNITY – Origin**

📢 Do you have a shocking story that will leave everyone jaw-dropped?

We’re creating a brand-new podcast for Origin, the platform where **women share their most intimate, powerful, and unforgettable real-life experiences.**

We're looking for women with extraordinary true stories: from being stalked, to extreme body modification, to unusual addictions, and beyond. If your story is shocking, unforgettable, or something people won't believe, we want to share it.

🎥 This is a** paid opportunity** and filming happens in a** London** studio.

If that sounds like you (or someone you know), get in touch!

📧 Send your video tape submission to: **[mireille.lee@upstream-media.co.uk](mailto:mireille.lee@upstream-media.co.uk)**

https://www.youtube.com/@_origin

the wait is over! we are now accepting submissions for our summer production of “Be More Chill!”

for full details, visit the link in our bio.

Simone Nathalia - Director/Choreographer
Taylor McKee - Music Director
Madison Raybould - Choreographer
Morgan Da Silva-Rolph - Stage Manager

audition dates
in-person: December 20th & 21st, 2025
callbacks: January 3rd, 2026
self-tapes: submissions due on Dec. 19th

audition venue:
Carousel Theatre for Young People, 1411 Cartwright St, Granville Island

audition requirements:
all roles in this production are volunteer, non-union. xoxo welcomes performers 18+ of all genders, ethnicities, and skill levels to audition.

what to prepare:
1. 2 contrasting musical theatre songs, (you may only be asked to sing one, but please have both ready).

2. a 1-2 minute contemporary, comedic monologue - this must be memorized.

how to apply:
please email your headshot and resume to theatre@xoxotv.ca to be scheduled with an audition time, or to request a self-tape submission.

character breakdowns can be found in our “audition package” link in bio.

production dates:
July 15th - 18th, 2026

production venue:
Firehall Arts Centre, 280 E Cordova St, Vancouver

notes:
rehearsals will begin April 30th, 2026
Saturdays 10:00am to 6:00pm
Tuesdays & Thursdays 6:00pm to 10:00pm

contact info@xoxotv.ca or DM us with any questions!

best of luck to all performers - we’ll see you at auditions! 😁💄🐾

Music and Lyrics by Joe Iconis
Book by Joe Tracz
Based on the Novel by Ned Vizzini

BE MORE CHILL is presented by arrangement with Concord Theatricals.
www.concordtheatricals.com
The world premiere production of Be More Chill was commissioned and originally produced by Two River Theater Company in Red Bank, NJ
John Dias, Artistic Director / Michael Hurst, Managing Director
This work was supported by a Theatre Commissioning and Production Initiative grant from the Doris Duke Charitable Foundation
Orchestrations and Arrangements by Charlie Rosen
.
.

CASTING CALL — Vancouver, BC (Union/Non-Union • Volunteer)

Project: BOYISH — 4th Year Capilano University Short Film

Director: Vlada Hayvoronska

Filming Dates: Feb 6–8, 2026

We’re casting MIA and SKIPPER, two key supporting roles in a gritty, character-driven coming-of-age short about the messy shift from boyhood to adulthood.

MIA (supporting)

Female, 16–18 age-presenting (actor must be 18+)

Luka’s older sister. Loud, messy, protective, insecure underneath. Pretends she’s tough but she’s still figuring life out.

SKIPPER (supporting)Male, 25–35

A not-so-charming burnout. Lives off beer, validation, and vibes. Thinks he’s the “wise older guy,” but he’s actually deeply stuck.

TO SUBMIT:

Email boyish2026@gmail.com

 with:

• headshot

• demo reel / clips

• subject line: BOYISH – MIA or BOYISH – SKIPPER

Deadline: Dec 14th, 2025 — 11:59 PM

Notes:

• Union & non-union performers welcome

• Volunteer project (student short; meals + credits provided)

• Must be 18+

• Diversity encouraged — all backgrounds welcome

items.text:
**CASTING CALL FOR A 10-MIN SHORT FILM**
Hi everyone! We’re seeking local actors for a neorealist short film shooting in late January in Vancouver. The film is intended for 2026 festival submissions.

**Logline:**

A college student volunteers on a visual-assist app to help an elderly man in his small apartment, unaware that a quiet glitch has turned their private calls into a public stream.

**Production Details**

• Location: Vancouver, BC

• Shoot Window: Late January – Early February 2026 (TBD)

• Genre: Neorealist Drama

• Non-Union / Volunteer

• Meals + IMDb credit provided

**ROLES**

**MAYA — Female, 19–24 (Open Ethnicity)**

Quiet, inward, emotionally guarded.
Minimal dialogue; performance driven by micro-reactions and natural handheld close-ups.
Must be comfortable with subtle, restrained acting.
Grounded student under stress — *Wendy & Lucy*, *Never Rarely Sometimes Always* tone.

**LEON — Male, 65–80 (Open Ethnicity)**

Soft-spoken, solitary, dignified.
Partially visually impaired; actor need not be visually impaired but must portray limited vision naturally.
Understated physicality: small gestures, hesitation, lived-in presence.

**TO APPLY**

Please send the following to **seetogetherfilm@gmail.com**
Subject: **“SEE TOGETHER – MAYA”** or **“SEE TOGETHER – LEON”**
• Recent headshot
• Short introduction (video or written)
• Availability (Jan–Feb 2026)
• Any naturalistic acting samples (if available)

We will cast people first through self-tapes.

Thank you!

We are casting for the 2026 Weird and Wonderful festival which will run between March 3rd and March 8th.

“Sardines” follows five sardines as they bicker over life's meaning and their purpose in the world. 

We are looking for 5 actors of any age or look who can comfortably play off of each others comedic timing.

If you are interested in auditioning for a role please send a self tape that you feel fits the criteria via we transfer / any other downloadable link to:

Seanrobinsonfreelance@gmail.com

Self tapes are due by 31st December and the cast will be contacted by the new year.

Please note: this is a 20 min play and will be part of a three play evening. A profit share will be paid.

items.text:
Do you have experience working with children and young people aged 6-18? Do you have a passion for musical theatre and dancing, singing and acting? Are you looking for an opportunity to combine your skills and interests to develop young people in a fun and professional setting? Then PQA Haywards Heath is just the place for you!

Due to the success of our growing academy, The Pauline Quirke Academy of Performing Arts (PQA), a leading provider of weekend performing arts training, is currently recruiting MUSICAL THEATRE TEACHER for their Academy in Haywards Heath on Saturday mornings and/or afternoons.

We are searching for fun, engaging and passionate individuals looking to bring lots of exciting and innovative ideas to our Musical Theatre module. If you are passionate about learning, the performing arts and making a positive impact on the lives of young people, we would be delighted to hear from you!

PQA follows safer recruiting. An enhanced DBS on the update service will be required and can be arranged. Applicants must be 18+.

To apply please email your CV with a cover letter explaining why you would be the ideal candidate for this role. Please send these direct to Principal Florence on florence.tingley@pqacademy.com.

We look forward to hearing from you!

We’re inviting influencers to join us for a barter collaboration, an exclusive filming & tasting experience at my Asian Restaurant (sushi, wok food, cocktail...)

Be part of our upcoming content featuring Girls’ Night, Family Night & Couples’ Night. Enjoy delicious food, a warm and candlelit atmosphere, and a way to meet new people

(The theme will be like in the pictures)

What we’re looking for:

👗 Neutral or elegant clothes

🎬 Comfortable on camera &  acting skills because we will film some contents with us (note that it will be a face-review)

Available on the 10th of December morning (the shooting and eating will be around 3-4 hours)

📲 Willing to post:

1 Instagram Story tagging us

1 Video showcasing our space & reviewing your experience with voice over uploading on your TikTok (5000 followers at least)

Perks:

✅ Complimentary food tasting and gift

✅ Featured on our social media

✅ A fun, creative day with us!

Spaces are limited — comment or DM my Instagram (@nvowi_ngvn) to secure your spot and be part of something special! I don't check Facebook messenger so please text me via Insta.

1-Bedroom Apartment for Rent – Budapest 7th District (Erzsébet körút 39)
💶 Rent: €750/month + utilities & common costs

items.text:
Hey everyone, my name is Alix 👋

I moved to Manchester on 3 November 2025 and I’m still learning my way around Salford and Manchester city centre! I don’t drive and I don’t currently have any travel passes, so I’m looking for opportunities that are walking distance or directly on Metrolink tram routes 🚊 in:

✅ Manchester city centre
✅ Salford areas (easy to reach by tram)

I’d really appreciate recommendations that are actually in tram zones or the city centre — tram + walking is my only way around right now.

A bit about me & my situation — I’m currently under Salford social services and sadly they’ve made it clear they won’t provide support, so I’m living up here with no support at all. My family live down south, I don’t know anyone here yet, and it’s been very isolating and lonely… but I’m staying proactive and positive 💛

🎭 My main passion is theatre and acting

I want to build experience onstage and backstage, especially in:

✨ Lighting & stage tech
🎨 Set/prop painting
🔧 Stagehand / backstage crew / stage tech
🍹 Theatre bar / FOH / front of house / bar work
🎬 Film & TV set experience in the future

Long-term dream:

🎬 Acting roles on film/TV sets
📺 Something like soap acting (Corrie style!)
🎥 TV & movie roles

I’ve tried contacting companies myself with no luck (emails, calls, social media, applications — all ignored ❌) but I’m not giving up.

✅ Availability: 7 days a week, mornings to evenings, any hours

I’m not here for sympathy — I just want someone to say:

💛 “I’ll give you a chance.”
💛 A place to volunteer, learn, and build experience
💛 Roles near the tram lines / city

Please feel free to:

📩 Message me
🏷️ Tag places or people
💬 Comment suggestions

Thank you so much for reading 🤍
Let’s make Manchester feel like home 🫶🚊🎭🐾

items.text:
Palmera Job Offer S26

Ready for the best summer of your life? Join our Entertainment Teams and work under the sun in beautiful Greece. ☀️🇬🇷

WE ARE LOOKING FOR PERFORMERS:

Position: (Aerialist, Acrobat, Juggler – performing shows at various hotels)
Contract Period: 1 May – 31 October 2026
Monthly Net Salary: From €1,000 - 1500€ (depending on experience, skills, and performance)
Employment Type: Swiss contract or self-employed freelancer

Venues: 4★ and 5★ hotels located on Kos, Crete, or Rhodes Island, Greece

Terms and Benefits
 • 1–2 weeks of free rehearsals prior to the contract start date, depending on the candidate’s progress in learning choreography
 • One day off per week
 • 1–2 performances per day( 1hour show )
 • Free accommodation and board at each hotel where performances take place, including meals in the main restaurant and beverages
 • Accident, pension, and social insurance coverage included
 • €300 travel bonus reimbursed with the final salary for six-month contracts
 • Free airport transfer upon arrival in Greece
 • Free internet and laundry services
 • Work uniforms and costumes provided
 • Company car available for work-related purposes
 • Additional performance bonus available at the end of the contract
 • Potential for career growth within the company and opportunities for contract renewal
 • An exceptional opportunity to gain professional and cultural experience under the Greek sun ☀

🎥 Watch our show productions:
https://youtu.be/9PdbLO–GX4?si=W8fKURLEWPjE9bCG

📩Apply Now for Online Auditions! Make Summer 2026 unforgettable — send your CV to: adriano@palmera-agency.com

Best regards,
Palmera Team
